reviews.text: Small cost convenient place for an happy hours.   It is small but service and prices are reasonable.  Just seat at the tables facing the street if u wanna smoke.
Nice bar where music is not very loud. Great place to have a conversation.
had murphy’s draught and some snacks. snacks just so-so... the good thing is it’s close to the times square.
200 $ extra charge just for seating, plus drinks. Was too expensive, otherwise ok place to have beers
A really normal bar you don't know why it exists... else than being down a building with a very good Japanese restaurant (message if you want the name...)
